      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1780213702268,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "GCReporting.API\n\n- For each dir fetch most recent xlsx file every x min\n- Compare file with last uploaded file. Two steps: 1) Timestamp changed? if yes 2) download and hash match.\n- if same break;\n- if different then mark it for upload",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "GCReporting.API\n\n- For each dir fetch most recent xlsx file every x min\n- Compare file with last uploaded file. Two steps: 1) Timestamp changed? if yes 2) download and hash match.\n- if same break;\n- if different then mark it for upload",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
